page.title: 15Birds Seen (May 84- May 85)
page.content: Blackbird, song thrush, house sparrow, goldfinch, rook, wood pigeon, jackdaw, woodpeckers (green, great spotted) fly catcher, black cap, tits (long tailed, blue, great) chaffinch, robin, yellow hammer, wren, sparrow hawk, partridge, pheasant, swallow, kestrel, collared dove, gulls (black-headed, herring), house martin, mistle thrush, moorhen, barn owl, swift, wagtails (pied, grey, yellow), dunnock, skylark, little owl, linnet, Canada goose, white throat, chiff-chaff, garden warbler, mallard, starling, magpie, lapwing, coot, reed bunting, heron, greenfinch, snipe, jay spotted flycatcher, snipe, goldcrest, common sandpiper, wood warbler, lesser white throat, tree creeper, crow, bull finch, redwing, fieldfare, stock dove, meadow pipit, stonechat, tufted duck, brambling. ...... 68 in total. {Sighted around Blackwater
